Package: bookworm
Title: Create and Manage Dataset Codebooks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Brady", family = "Rippon", email = "brr7014@med.cornell.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bookworm provides a framework for creating and applying dataset metadata using readable YAML codebooks. 
    It supplies variable labels and value mapping and further extends to factor ordering, validation rules, units, and privacy management. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bradyrippon/bookworm
BugReports: https://github.com/bradyrippon/bookworm/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    yaml,
    labelled
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rmarkdown,
    knitr,
    gt,
    gtsummary
Encoding: UTF-8
